Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96034,97910}He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102457,105376}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:47.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105710,107295}Congratulations, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116346,119432}We're looking forward to\Nyour wedding ceremony tomorrow, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119432,120808}We wish you happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123227,125605}The blackboard is\Nfor teaching purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:08.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125605,128232}It's not to be doodled on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128232,129651}What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129651,131194}Get out your notebooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:13.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131194,133029}Class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:16.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133780,136783}"You remind me\Nof the early summer days,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136783,140411}but you are even more\Nbeautiful and delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:24.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140411,144374}The wind of May\Ngently takes flower seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144374,146668}Only in the summer…"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149212,151881}Good. That should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151881,153466}We can now make a bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153466,155426}The bride will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155802,158888}It wouldn't kill Mr. Curry to show\Nsome enthusiasm, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158888,161474}We even prepared a party\Nin the classroom for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:43.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161474,163851}Well, that's just how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:47.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163851,167522}Imagine him all smiley.\NHonestly, that would creep me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167522,169524}You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:53.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172151,173945}Mary will be overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173945,175279}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:59.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175279,179534}I'd like to deliver it to Mary personally,\Nand congratulate her while I'm at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179534,182412}She's at Robert's place right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182412,185039}They're talking about\Nmoving in, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185039,187417}So, want me to keep it\Nuntil she's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187417,188584}No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:12.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188584,192213}We'll just go to them now\Nand give it to Ms. Marry ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:15.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193923,195717}What's there\Nto laugh about, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:21.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197510,201431}Just think about it. We're going to see\NMr. Curry and Ms. Mary together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:26.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201431,206185}I got it! We'll get to see how he's like\Nwhen he's with his fiancée!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:26.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206185,206853}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206853,207937}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218281,220283}We'll be standing at the altar\Nat this time tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:40.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220283,220992}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:46.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225037,226330}Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226330,227290}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227290,228082}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229792,231085}Is something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234046,236591}Haven't you forgotten\Nabout something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237383,238926}Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:00.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238926,240595}Yes, something\Nvery, very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241095,242972}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242972,246100}The preparations\Nfor the wedding are finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246100,248186}We're all packed\Nfor the honeymoon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.18,0:04:09.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248186,249312}That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:11.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249312,251189}That's not what you meant…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253483,256319}I know! I did forget\Nabout one thing, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256319,257361}Did you just realize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:19.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257361,259071}It's the rings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:24.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260948,264911}I wanted to put them in the suit\NI'm going to wear tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264911,267246}so that I would not\Nforget them by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268289,269832}We are buttoned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269832,271125}Are you absolutely sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:31.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271125,271751}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272251,275046}Isn't there something else\Nyou forgot about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275046,277340}Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:39.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277340,279967}It is the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279967,281177}You haven't done it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281177,282011}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:46.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283095,286098}I can't marry you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:46.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286098,286849}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289560,292480}Things are taking a strange turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294690,296734}Stop this tomfoolery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296734,298694}It's no tomfoolery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298694,300571}If you don't have any idea\Nwhat I'm talking about…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:02.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300571,302865}Yes. I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:06.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303908,306619}I will not go with you to the altar.\NMark my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:13.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309747,313417}You're just nervous\Nbefore the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313417,315795}Let's get you home.\NYou should take rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315795,317421}I'll walk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317421,319924}I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:20.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:319924,320675}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320675,322218}Oh… Be careful on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325888,327473}I am very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327807,329684}Yes, yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:33.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329684,333062}Let's talk about it\Nafter the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:52.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351289,352623}Ms. Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:352623,353499}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354250,356002}It's you, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:04.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:362425,364010}It smells so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364010,365094}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365094,367555}– Ms. Mary…\N– Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367555,370391}We overheard that you might\Ncancel the wedding tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:12.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371225,372852}Were you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373269,375521}Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375521,376856}I think I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377315,379358}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:21.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379817,381027}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381027,382320}Could it be…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:26.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382320,386490}Could it be that you don't like\NMr. Curry anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386490,388576}I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389952,391871}That is the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:36.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392788,396042}I feel bad for Mr. Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396042,399420}While I agree that\Nhe's a very strict person
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399420,402173}and it's not very fun\Nto be around him—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:44.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402173,404258}John, don't say this to Ms. Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404258,405468}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:49.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405801,409597}John, while it is true\Nthat he is a strict person,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:52.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409597,412975}but he is the most upstanding\Nand honest person I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:57.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413517,417688}Besides, even he\Nis not always serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.68,0:07:02.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417688,422360}When he's reading his favorite poems,\Nhe has the sweetest smile in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422360,423611}Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424987,426822}Yeah. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426822,428157}I'm sorry, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:11.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428157,431035}This is not something\NI want to talk about to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:14.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431035,434997}Come on, Ms. Mary.\NIf you want, we can give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:17.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434997,437208}Yeah. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:21.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437208,441295}I may be bad at talking,\Nbut I'm good at listening to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443464,444507}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446842,448344}You see…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457061,459105}Say, Dad…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459105,460523}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460940,462274}Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464276,465695}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465695,466946}You can ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466946,468322}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:51.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469657,471075}Do you love Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472076,473828}Where did this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474036,475079}Just answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475621,478416}Of course I love your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478416,480209}And I love you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480209,483462}Are you able to tell her\Nthat directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483462,485089}Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486841,488926}What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:09.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488926,489635}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489635,490594}John, talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:11.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490594,491846}It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500062,502314}Look, darling.\NIt's such a beautiful morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502314,503774}Wake up and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:26.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505526,506610}Get ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506610,508070}The wedding ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509947,512533}Oh, today is Robert's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512533,514577}It's a perfect day for a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515745,517038}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517038,519081}John, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:42.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519582,522084}Oh? Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522460,523711}Lassie, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555618,556494}Mary…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556494,557828}Oh? It's you, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558537,560331}An early bird, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:20.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560331,560956}Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:21.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560956,561707}Where's Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562208,564210}Isn't she in the waiting room?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564210,566253}You haven't seen her today yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:29.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567797,569256}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:35.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569256,575221}It's bad luck for the bride and the groom\Nto see each other before the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575221,579433}Naturally, I don't believe\Nin such superstitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579433,580976}But she's not in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:43.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581102,583687}Maybe she's still asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:46.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583687,586565}It's fine. There's plenty of time\Ntill the ceremony starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586565,587983}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:588484,589610}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592905,594532}So she hasn't come yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603582,606210}What am I supposed to write here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606210,607753}"Dear Robert".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607753,609547}"Dear Robert"…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609547,611173}Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611590,612883}It's almost ten o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:15.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612883,615511}We have only half an hour\Nbefore the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615511,616679}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618222,621600}I feel much better\Nafter talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622685,624061}Who do we have here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625688,627898}Congratulations, Mr. Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627898,629650}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629650,631861}I'm so jealous, you bad boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:32.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631861,632862}I'm not a bad boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633237,634655}Mary is sure taking her time…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634655,636699}Mary? She's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636699,637449}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637449,638450}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638450,640953}She should be dressing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:44.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642204,644165}I'm sorry.\NExcuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646417,648294}Do you know where Mary is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648294,649712}Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:53.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649712,653591}Mary left the house\Nlong before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:54.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653591,654675}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654675,655676}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663309,664852}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666395,667479}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667479,668480}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670274,672401}Why Mary is not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672401,675029}That is something\NI would like to know myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:16.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675029,676655}Anything happened\Nbetween you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677823,680784}I can't marry you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681243,682536}I am very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683370,684914}Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684914,685831}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:30.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685831,690502}Congratulations, congratulations!\NI'm so happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:33.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690502,693839}How is the bride's father\Nfeeling right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693839,695216}Come with me, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:52.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709480,712107}You're the Carracloughs' dog, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:55.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712107,715069}You can't enter the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:56.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715069,716362}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716362,718280}What's that? Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:00.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718280,720783}"To Robert Curry"…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720783,722868}I recognize this handwriting…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723285,724578}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:06.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724578,726121}It's a letter from Mary!
Comment: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:10.91,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:730918,730918}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735923,739093}It's a letter from Mary!\NWhat did she write?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739677,741136}Good, he's got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741136,743597}Quick, open the envelope\Nand read what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:26.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745099,746600}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746600,748227}Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:31.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748227,751146}Oh, Mother, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751146,752773}You made it, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755818,757486}Never mind them,\Njust read the letter…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758487,760572}Our child is getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:44.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760572,764243}Even if we were on the other side of Earth,\Nthere is no way we could miss that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764243,766537}Where did you hide\Nyour cute fiancée?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:47.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766537,767913}I'd love to finally meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:50.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768872,770666}Well, about that…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770666,773711}She forgot something\Nand she went to get it real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773711,775713}While wearing a wedding dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:57.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775713,777423}Yes, which is why\Nit's taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778340,779341}This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779341,781593}Just read it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781593,785347}I apologize for the late introduction.\NI am Mary's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785347,787016}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787016,788726}Right, the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:10.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789518,790519}Congratulations, Mr. Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:11.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790519,791729}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791729,794023}Ah, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794023,795399}Where is your bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795399,796650}Is it okay for us to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796650,799320}She… went to get something\Nshe had forgotten…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799653,801113}Is he going to read it or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803073,804366}What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:27.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804366,807161}The priest will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807161,808620}What do you suggest, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809413,810622}I'm not your dad yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:32.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811040,812124}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812750,816378}If I knew this would happen, I'd seriously\Nreconsider letting my daughter marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816754,819381}Now is not the time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:41.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819381,821717}Congratulations,\NMr. Rice, Mr. Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:46.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822676,826847}Nope. He completely\Nforgot about the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:53.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830392,833062}All the guests\Nmust've arrived by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:55.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833062,835397}I'm sure the teacher\Nis drenching in sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837608,839651}Was it the right thing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:01.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840110,841862}You can't back out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:04.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841862,844990}Or are you telling me\Nit's okay to marry him as is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844990,846575}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846575,847993}It's not, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:34.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872935,874895}What on earth is Mary doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874895,876313}Why didn't she come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876313,879775}It's not like we had a bad fight\Nor anything yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885489,886615}Mary…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:886615,888784}Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892579,894164}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897376,899294}Right, the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:02.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900546,902589}Good! Now read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:08.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906093,908887}"I'll be waiting for you\Nin our special spot."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909471,910431}Mary…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913434,914601}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919398,920607}Let's go with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:21.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920607,921358}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:26.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923694,926864}Mary! Mary! Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926864,928407}Ah, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929032,930909}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:32.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931827,932619}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934455,935664}Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935664,937124}Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937124,938584}Right to your special spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:41.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940419,941503}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941503,943088}That's not the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943088,944798}School is in the other direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:47.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944798,947050}Mr. Curry got the wrong place…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:50.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947885,950512}Don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:56.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953140,956477}I thought that he'd know in a flash\Nthe place Ms. Mary meant…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956477,958479}But he doesn't have\Nthe slightest idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:958770,961690}Since when was Mr. Curry\Nsuch a fast runner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:08.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966945,968906}I'm in a hurry, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968906,970991}I don't have time\Nto play with you—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975412,976455}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976455,978290}That's the wedding rings you took!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978290,979416}You crazy dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980834,982044}Well done, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986048,987674}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006902,1008862}What are we doing in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009655,1011990}Lassie! Cut it out, will you…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:57.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016328,1017621}Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018705,1019873}I finally know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019873,1022668}The thing I was supposed\Nto say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022668,1023752}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023752,1026338}Yes. It's about the wallpaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026338,1028966}It can be green like you wanted.\NI don't mind it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028966,1030634}Wallpaper?…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030634,1031760}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031760,1033262}That wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033262,1034304}Then how's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034304,1037015}You're always looking after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037015,1038475}Looking after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038475,1041353}I will fix all the flaws in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041353,1043438}I'll sort all my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043438,1046066}I will make sure to brush\Nmy teeth after every meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:29.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046066,1049570}I will be careful not to\Nmake a mess when eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:30.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049570,1050737}I will keep my nails short…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050737,1052364}He's like a kid…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052990,1055951}So, please, Mary. Don't be angry\Nwith me anymore and marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1055951,1057286}Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057286,1058245}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:42.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059371,1062291}I'm not angry over\Nsuch trivial things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:45.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063083,1065335}So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:50.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066628,1070132}This is the place where we talked\Nfor the first time. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:53.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070132,1073552}I came to deliver bread\Nfor the picnic you had here at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:55.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073552,1075429}So that was it…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075429,1077222}"So that was it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:18:00.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077222,1080684}Aren't you here because I told you\Nto come to our special spot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:06.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080684,1086315}No, actually, at first I thought\Nyou meant the Berry Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:09.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086315,1089484}But Lassie took the rings\Nand I chased her down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089735,1090777}Right, the rings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091153,1092779}Give them back, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:17.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095324,1097075}Robert…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:19.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098285,1099494}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:23.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099494,1103290}Remember how I told you that you forgot\Nto say the most important thing to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:24.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103290,1104875}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105959,1108879}You said the same thing yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108879,1110297}Not just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:32.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110297,1112507}Do you realize how many times\NI had asked you about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:35.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112507,1115385}No… I don't think I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:40.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116762,1120599}The thing I forgot.\NThe thing I forgot…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:42.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121850,1122893}How about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:46.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122893,1126063}Why do you want to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:50.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126063,1130233}Well, it's because you're beautiful\Nand good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130233,1132944}You are interested in books,\Nand have good sense of wallpapers—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:56.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132944,1136073}These aren't the words\NI want to hear! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:57.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136073,1137449}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137449,1139493}So, maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139493,1141620}Marriage between a man\Nand a woman is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:05.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141620,1145624}Well, it signifies\Nestablishment of a family…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145624,1147250}Which means…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:13.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151797,1153799}Let me ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153799,1156677}Why do you want to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161306,1162683}That's because…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162683,1163809}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163809,1166687}This is because you're\Nlike a world class pianist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:31.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167062,1171066}When your white fingers play on the piano that\Nis my heart, a beautiful melody comes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171066,1172734}When I hear it, everything—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172734,1175112}That's a line from some book!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175112,1178073}I want to hear you say it\Nin your own words!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178073,1180409}I don't care about some quotes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:44.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180409,1184913}I just want you to tell me in your own way\Nwhat are your feelings for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:48.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187332,1188709}I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:49.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189126,1189960}What have you just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192087,1193422}I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193422,1194423}I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194715,1196758}I'm in love with you, Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196758,1198218}That's why I want to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207686,1209354}You said it, at long last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210313,1213734}You never told me this before,\Nnot even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213734,1215610}I didn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215610,1216486}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216486,1218155}So that's what it was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:18.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218155,1218864}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220991,1222993}It's okay, Lassie.\NYou can give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:25.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224119,1225704}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225704,1226580}So…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226580,1228206}You also…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:28.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228206,1228749}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229791,1231752}I'm in love with you, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231752,1233086}I will marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234463,1236173}Congratulations, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236173,1238091}Congratulations!\NI wish you a happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:41.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238091,1241303}Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242679,1244181}Where did you come from, children?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:51.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248602,1251730}Remember to fold\Nyour clothes well, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251730,1253315}Make sure you brush\Nyour teeth well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253690,1256026}To think it's you\Nwho's looking after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:58.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256276,1258403}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258779,1260030}Oh, children…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284930,1286765}Throw the bouquet, Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286765,1287516}Over here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:30.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287516,1290936}Whoever picks up the bouquet\Nwill be the next bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290936,1292687}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299110,1300779}Lassie…
