Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:06.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322592,1326179}{\i1}And they have a huge elephant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:09.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326179,1329266}{\i1}But it's treated badly\Nand seems very scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329266,1330934}{\i1}And then…
